## ‚öôÔ∏è Installation

**From PyPI (recommended):**

```bash
pip install cosmolib
```

**From source (for developers and contributors):**

```bash
git clone https://github.com/astro-ph/cosmolib.git
cd cosmolib
pip install -e .
```

